Assembler Syntax

AE_NAND aed0..15(ae_dr_to_dr_v), aed0..15(ae_dr_to_dr_v0), aed0..15(ae_dr_to_dr_v1)

C Syntax

#include <xtensa/tie/xt_hifi2.h>

extern ae_int64 AE_NAND(ae_int64 d0, ae_int64 d1);

Description

AE_NAND performs a bitwise NAND on d0 and d1, with results to d.

Implementation Pipeline

In Out
ae_dr_to_dr_v0 Mstage, ae_dr_to_dr_v1 Mstage ae_dr_to_dr_v Mstage
